description: Demolition of all existing buildings and structures on site and the mixed-use redevelopment of the site to provide two buildings of ground-plus 43 and ground-plus 57 storeys respectively plus lower ground floor and basement levels, including 669 residential units (Use Class C3), 6,782 sqm GIA of hotel use (Use Class C1), and 733 sqm GIA of commercial, business and service use (Use Class E), podium level, car and cycle parking, refuse and service areas, access, hard and soft landscaping, public realm and highway works and other works associated with the development. The application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement.
